are transcendental and have no material effect. One is therefore filled with peace in Kṛṣṇa consciousness. But one who is entangled in profit calculation for sense gratification cannot have that peace. This is the secret of Kṛṣṇa consciousness – realization that there is no existence besides Kṛṣṇa is the platform of peace and fearlessness.76:[\"$\",\"div\",\"1624-purport,1624-purport\",{\"className\":\"av-purport\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\""])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-center em:leading-5 em:text-xl font-bold em:mb-4\",\"children\":\"Purport\"}],[[\"$\",\"$L3f\",\"child-1629\",{\"child\":\"$2b:props:children:0:props:children:props:page:child_items:0:children:10:child_items:4:children:0\",\"hasId\":true,\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"em:mb-4 em:leading-8 em:text-base s-justify\",\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"$d0\"}}]}]]]}]\n77:[\"$\",\"div\",\"1630-devanagari,1630-devanagari\",{\"className\":\"av-devanagari\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-center em:leading-5 em:text-xl font-bold em:mb-4 hidden\",\"children\":\"Devanagari\"}],[[\"$\",\"$L3f\",\"child-1631\",{\"child\":\"$2b:props:children:0:props:children:props:page:child_items:0:children:11:child_items:0:children:0\",\"hasId\":true,\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"em:mb-4 em:leading-8 em:text-lg text-center\",\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"सर्वकर्माणि मनसा सन्न्यस्यास्ते सुखं वशी ।\u003cbr/\u003eनवद्वारे पुरे देही नैव कुर्वन्न कारयन् ॥ १३ ॥\"}}]}]]]}]\n78:[\"$\",\"div\",\"1630-verse_text,1630-verse_text\",{\"className\":\"av-verse_text\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-center em:leading-5 em:text-xl font-bold em:mb-4 hidden\",\"children\":\"Verse text\"}],[[\"$\",\"$L3f\",\"child-1632\",{\"child\":\"$2b:props:children:0:props:children:props:page:child_items:0:children:11:child_items:1:children:0\",\"hasId\":true,\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"em:mb-4 